    <h1>Brand Recognition</h1>
    <p class="description">A consumer's ability to identify your brand when shown a cue — logo, color, jingle, packaging, or name. The <strong>aided</strong> half of brand awareness, and the entry point to every downstream demand metric.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
